details.description: A slow moving Monday morning. A fast paced Wednesday lunch break. An easy and pleasant Saturday afternoon. No matter where you are in your week (or your day), you can count on Salted Melon to have exactly what you need, sometimes before you know you need it.

reviews_data.review_text:
What a breath of fresh air in SouthPark!!

On behalf of the Hampton Inn and Suites at Phillips Place; we are so delighted to welcome our new neighbor to the shopping center. Hannah and Thomas were so amazing and sent us some catering options to our staff to sample and we were blown away. From their breakfast burritos to their steak sandwiches and buffalo bowls we couldn't stop raving about the tenderness of the meats and flavor packed into every dish. Their presentation for catering was bright, exciting and well put together. Their catering options left us craving more; we picked up lunch their opening week and were greeted with polite and fast service along with bright decor and even better vibes.

This is the perfect stop for in-between zoom calls or a refreshing lunch outing with the family this summer. So excited to keep sampling their menu and promote to all of our guests.
